	* dump-parse-tree.cc (show_omp_namelist): Add iterator support for
	OMP_LIST_MAP.
	* match.cc (gfc_free_omp_namelist): Free namespace in namelist for
	OMP_LIST_MAP.
	* openmp.cc (gfc_match_omp_clauses): Parse 'iterator' modifier for
	'map' clause.
